  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Videographer",
  "description": "<h3>About Mofunland</h3><p>Mofunland is a creative learning playground that combines <strong>puzzle-solving, brain training, competitions, camps, and events</strong>.<br />We work with <strong>students, families, professionals, and international partners</strong>, and regularly organize <strong>competitions, camps, cruises, and large-scale events</strong>.</p><p>We are looking for a <strong>Videographer</strong> who is passionate about storytelling, fast-paced content, and capturing real moments — not just “nice shots”.</p><h2>🎯 Key Responsibilities</h2><h3>🎬 Video Shooting</h3><ul><li><p>Shoot high-quality videos for:</p><ul><li><p>Events & competitions (cubing tournaments, camps, showcases)</p></li><li><p>Classes & training sessions</p></li><li><p>Brand content & promotional videos</p></li><li><p>Short-form content (TikTok / IG Reels / YouTube Shorts)</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Handle camera setup, lighting, audio, and basic on-site troubleshooting</p></li></ul><h3>✂️ Video Editing</h3><ul><li><p>Edit videos into engaging formats for different platforms:</p><ul><li><p>Short-form (30s–90s)</p></li><li><p>Highlight reels</p></li><li><p>Promo videos</p></li><li><p>Simple storytelling videos</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Add basic motion graphics, subtitles, sound effects, and music where needed</p></li></ul><h3>📱 Social Media Content Support</h3><ul><li><p>Work closely with marketing team to:</p><ul><li><p>Repurpose footage into multiple content pieces</p></li><li><p>Suggest content angles & hooks</p></li><li><p>Capture behind-the-scenes moments</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Understand platform styles (TikTok ≠ Instagram ≠ YouTube)</p></li></ul><h3>🎨 Creative Contribution</h3><ul><li><p>Propose video ideas, shot lists, and content formats</p></li><li><p>Help improve overall video quality & storytelling</p></li><li><p>Keep up with trends (especially short-form & youth content)</p></li></ul><h2>🧠 Requirements</h2><h3>✅ Must-Have</h3><ul><li><p>Proven experience as a Videographer / Video Editor</p></li><li><p>Comfortable with <strong>event shooting</strong> and fast-moving environments</p></li><li><p>Skilled in video editing software (e.g. Premiere Pro, Final Cut Pro, CapCut, DaVinci Resolve)</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently and meet deadlines</p></li><li><p>Strong sense of storytelling and pacing</p></li></ul><h3>👍 Nice-to-Have</h3><ul><li><p>Experience shooting <strong>education, kids, sports, or events</strong></p></li><li><p>Familiar with TikTok / IG Reels style editing</p></li><li><p>Basic photography skills</p></li><li><p>Own equipment (camera, lens, mic) – <em>optional</em></p></li></ul><h2>💡 Personality Fit </h2><ul><li><p>Energetic, proactive, and responsible</p></li><li><p>Comfortable working with kids, parents, and event crowds</p></li><li><p>Able to adapt quickly during live events</p></li><li><p>Passion for creativity, learning, or youth culture is a big plus</p></li></ul>",
  "minimumYearsExperience": 3,
